Class FileSystemElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileSystemElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Directory, File
    public abstract class FileSystemElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an abstract element within a file system, providing common properties and methods. This class serves as a base for more specific file system elements like files and directories.
